SQL_STMT_U.val: select TMPL_ID from :1/TMPL join :1/ADMN on ADMN_NO = TMPL_ADMNO and ADMN_TYPEGLPACKAGE = 3 join :1/LDGR on LDGR_ADMNO = TMPL_ADMNO and LDGR_NO = TMPL_LEDG_NO and (LDGR_LEDGERTYPE = 4 or LDGR_LEDGERTYPE = 5) where TMPL_RUNNUMBER = :2 and TMPL_CURRENCY <> 'RON' and (TMPL_AMOUNTDEBITC <> 0 or TMPL_AMOUNTCREDITC <> 0) for fetch only
